00:15:41.780 --> 00:15:43.940
data traversing that network.

00:15:44.170 --> 00:15:49.380
So it now means that remotely I can have
access to massive amounts of data that's

00:15:49.380 --> 00:15:55.240
encrypted at rest on the server and I may
have a very low bandwidth connection,

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:58.580
but I have full access to
that data on my mobile device,

00:15:58.700 --> 00:15:58.800
right?

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:04.040
So I'm no longer relying on a sole
