00:16:07.390 --> 00:16:10.000
on the drive and if it gets stolen.

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:15.000
So now during use of that data,
I have access to it across the network.

00:16:15.410 --> 00:16:18.250
That's been quite helpful
to a lot of folks.

00:16:18.570 --> 00:16:19.840
Things that are near
