00:16:50.670 --> 00:16:54.700
and super computer capabilities,
even on our own systems,

00:16:54.700 --> 00:16:57.180
is the ability to crack passwords
if you're trying to protect

00:16:57.330 --> 00:17:00.420
things just with passwords alone.

00:17:00.440 --> 00:17:04.240
Moving to a two-factor authentication,
solutions like smart cards,

00:17:04.280 --> 00:17:09.740
give you a significant protection,
really with reduced

00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:11.940
or limited complexity.

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:15.110
for systems.

00:17:15.960 --> 00:17:19.700
I want to take the smart card piece just
