Ty those two together with the smart
cards and the key thing is that

00:17:40.460 --> 00:17:44.900
we're trying to give you multiple
forms of strong authentication built

00:17:44.900 --> 00:17:48.730
on the platform that you can tie
into whatever directory service

00:17:48.730 --> 00:17:50.470
that you have on the back end.

00:17:50.540 --> 00:17:53.270
As I just mentioned,
I want to highlight the smart

00:17:53.380 --> 00:17:55.000
card piece here real quick.

00:17:55.080 --> 00:17:57.770
And that is with the integration
work that we've done,

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:01.200
you can now leverage that single
form of two-factor authentication,

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:05.200
that smart card,
for obviously logging into your system,

00:18:05.310 --> 00:18:09.800
for system administration,
the unlocking of screen saver, typical,

00:18:09.800 --> 00:18:13.790
sign encrypting of email, VPN,
