00:41:11.800 --> 00:41:16.920
it's also a very handy way to give out
a whole lot of personal information in

00:41:16.920 --> 00:41:22.780
one package if you lose it or it gets
stolen or it's compromised when it's not.

00:41:22.800 --> 00:41:28.470
So sensitive personal information or
company information should never be

00:41:28.470 --> 00:41:34.070
stored on the iPhone or should at the
very least be kept to a bare minimum.

00:41:34.100 --> 00:41:37.790
This includes information
stored in the notes application.

00:41:37.790 --> 00:41:41.320
And it includes things like
usernames and passwords,

00:41:41.430 --> 00:41:44.620
account numbers,
personal data and proprietary

00:41:44.620 --> 00:41:46.590
information among others.

