Choose a strong password
if you have to use it,

00:43:47.500 --> 00:43:50.660
and avoid performing any
sensitive transactions.

00:43:54.470 --> 00:43:57.780
Do not connect to unknown
wireless networks.

00:43:57.890 --> 00:44:01.300
A good example of this
